item.title: Drenched duathletes dominate Gravesend
item.author: Samuel Jackson,
item.description: As the first month of 2016 came to a close, eleven duathletes from Imperial College London battled against the elements to achieve an impressive tally of podium finishes at the Gravesend Winter Duathlon.
